records.name: Villa Nautica Paradise Island Resort

descriptions.direction: Located in Lankanfinolhu, Villa Nautica Paradise Island Resort is on the beach. Boutique by Island Breeze and Orofini Jewellery are worth checking out if shopping is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Paradise Island Beach and Kani Beach. With windsurfing and surfing/body boarding nearby, you'll find plenty of adventures in the water.
descriptions.general: Located at North Male' Atoll, only 9.6 km away from Velana International Airport, which takes approximately 20 minutes by speedboat. Places of interest include the Bandos (7.5 km), Hulhumale (9 km) and Vihamanaafushi (8 km). Facilities and services include restaurants, bars, cafe, spa facilities (extra charge), massage (extra charge), sauna (extra charge), credit cards accepted, free Wi-Fi/internet access, swimming pool, children's play area, children's pool, conference room, gym/fitness center, shop, laundry facilities, multilingual staff and babysitting services (extra charge). The rooms feature 24h room service, in-room safe, cable/satellite TV, towels provided, air conditioning, ceiling fan, telephone, minibar, hairdryer, terrace, coffee/tea maker, private bathroom and shower. Check-in Time: 14:00hrs of the arrival date Check-out Time: 12:00hrs of the departure date *In case of no show, early departure or reduction of stay, 100% full stay will be charged. **Please note that some of the above facilities may be closed due to weather / seasonal conditions.** Please note: Villa Nautica Paradise Island has a dedicated counter with a representative to greet and guide the guests on their onward journey - Counter No: E10. Note: Upon arrival at Velana International Airport, hotel representatives will welcome guests at the counter and assist them with speedboat transfers to Villa Nautica. Address: North Male Atoll, Lankanfinolhu, Maldives.
